      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个流量入口的故障转移流程。核心是IngressController和LoadBalancer之间的协作关系。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer"
