    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，IngressController作为入口，LoadBalancer做负载均衡。它们之间是什么关系？是单向依赖还是有条件分支？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "应该有个判断节点。先让IngressController指向LoadBalancer，但LoadBalancer本身要做一个决策——健康检查通过的话走正常路径，失败的话要回退。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "所以LoadBalancer既是节点又是判断条件？我理解为B节点做决策，Yes分支到正常的LoadBalancer处理，No分支回退到IngressController重试？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_LoadBalancer",
        "Infra_IngressController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，就是这个逻辑。Yes走C节点，No走D节点，最后C和D都汇聚到同一个出口E。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_LoadBalancer",
        "Infra_IngressController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把主结构搭出来：A是IngressController，指向B这个判断节点，B分出Yes到C、No到D，最后C和D都连到E。",
      "elements_involved": [
