      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "C和D的标签要准确。C是健康的LoadBalancer实例，D是回退到IngressController本身。E是最终的统一出口，代表请求被处理完成。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_LoadBalancer",
